    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price, this vehicle offers strong value for a buyer seeking an affordable daily driver or project opportunity. It starts, runs, and delivers the kind of straightforward utility that makes it a smart choice for commuting, local errands, or a second vehicle. Priced to sell and represented with confidence, it\u2019s a practical way to get on the road without overspending.",
