    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy runabout, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s got honest character, a practical feel, and a price that makes sense. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
