    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, no-nonsense driver/project with solid enthusiast upside. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, starts reliably, and the chassis still feels planted enough to enjoy on back roads or use as a budget commuter. It shows age cosmetically and will benefit from sorting, but it presents as a straightforward, mechanical car rather than a mystery. Great candidate for someone who appreciates a usable platform with character, serviceable fundamentals, and room to improve over time. Priced to move for the buyer who wants real hardware instead of overpolished fluff.",
      "price": 7900.0,
